+.TH DAG2ANY 1
+.SH NAME
+dag2any
+\- DAG to any data converter
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+.B dag2any
+.RB [[ \-o | \-\-prefix "]\ \fIfile_prefix\fP]
+.RB [ \- [ no ] stat ]
+.RB [ \- [ no ] parallelism ]
+.RB [ \- [ no ] sqlite ]
+.RB [ \- [ no ] text ]
+.RB [ \- [ no ] shrink ]
+.I dag-file
+.PP
+.SH DESCRIPTION
+dag2any converts
+.I .dag
+file generated by the dag recorder into various other formats,
+most importantly to text and sqlite3 database for further analysis.
